PMK Group, the leading manufacturer and distributor in electrical controlling panel, low voltage and medium voltage electrical products, has been officially established since 1981 with the solidly continuous growth under the name of PMK Corporation Ltd. and PMK Industry Co.,Ltd.; we serve all valued clients in both private and public sectors including residential and commercial buildings, hospital, utilities and factories. continuous developing our products and services to be the best in its class.
